title: Location, Community, Quality Living! It Starts Here!
posting_body: ['Location, Community, Quality Living!', 'It Starts Here!', 'Price: $3,100', 'Property Type: Apartment', 'Bedrooms: Studio', 'Bathrooms: 1.0', 'Pets: Pets OK', 'Building Amenities', 'Doorman', 'Elevator', 'Health Club', 'Garage', 'Subway', 'Diplomats OK', 'Laundry', 'Valet', 'Roof Deck', 'WiFi', 'Common Outdoor Space', 'Concierge', 'Apartment Amenities', 'Dishwasher', 'Hardwood', 'High Ceilings', 'Renovated', 'Granite Kitchen', 'Light', 'Microwave', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Open Kitchen', 'City View', 'This Unit with a Spacious Layout welcomes you home to Beautiful Hardwood Flooring, High Beamed 11" Ceilings, Knee to Ceiling Windows allowing Natural Light to reach every inch of this unit.', 'The Modern Kitchen is Designed with Maple Cabinetry and Stunning Counter Tops with updated and Energy Efficient State of the Art Stainless Steel Appliances.', 'Unwind in your Marble Bathroom with Soaking Tub and Custom Vanity leaving you with a smile on your face every night.', '-All', 'Pictures Are To Reference Finishes-', '~Amenities~', '- Fully equipped gym', '- 24/7 Doorman', '- Roof deck', '- on site super', '- laundry in building', '- Elevator', '~The Neighborhood~', 'Conveniently located in the heart of the Financial District just minutes away from Battery Park, The One World Trade Center and the Oculus.', 'It is also conveniently surrounded by shopping centers, supermarkets, fine dining and amazing entertainment destinations.', 'The 2,3,A,C,4,5,J, and Z subway lines are close by giving you easy access to the rest of the city.', '~Contact~', 'Daniel Bernabe', '929 928 5855', 'Any Questions Do Not Hesitate To Call Or Text Me At Anytime']
